name: Nunu Waterfall
address: Jl. Tanah Lot No.25, Pandak Bandung, Kec. Kediri, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1: The most stunning peaceful hidden gem, a short walk down and along the river. Secretly hidden so not tonnes of tourists find it easily. Its a short walk down some jungle style steps, walk down to the temple at the bottom and then a left turn and you can cross the river to get to it. Guide from Nunu showed us the way.
review 2: No way to get there. We even asked locals and unless you walk through trash and hope you dont randomly fall down somewhere, not easily accessible.
review 3: I can’t find this place, even the locals didn’t know about this waterfall:(
review 4: Loved it! Totally worth the visit.
